<br>
Give me a Bonecaster Robe over this any day.<br>
<br>
Simply put, the reagent is too expensive for what Rune IV does.  Rune III costs 10% of the money, minimal Mana (its a 34th spell), casts faster than most high-end Cleric Heals, and gives 60-75% of the protection of Rune IV.<br>
<br>
If you stack Rune III and Berserker Spirit you get better protection than Rune IV for less money and comparable Mana.  And Rune V makes Rune IV completely irrelevant.<br>
<br>
And the slow casting time pretty well negates the &quot;zero mana cost&quot; advantage.<br>
<br>
I hope the robe at least looks nice.<br>
<br>
Eidolon Faer<br>
